description: Immaculate one bedroom residence with great skyline views AND deeded garage parking! This is a super efficiently laid out condo, which accommodates both a living room set and a dining table. A great little entertaining space! The contemporary red kitchen provides a pop of color and the high ceilings and the oversized windows really bring that downtown view into the unit.  An in-unit washer/dryer closet and another closet which is outfitted with a custom office space complete the main living area. The bedroom area is outfitted with a custom closet including drawers and great storage .  A lovely modern bathroom with a floating vanity, sleek tile and a glass shower enclosure finish the space off.   All of this in an incredible location with restaurants, cafe's, boutique fitness facilities and the Red Line T right across the street. The Macallen offers 24/7 concierge, gym, outdoor pool and BBQ area's!  A true lifestyle facility!   Don't miss out!
